of School</i>. (4th ed.) Harry K.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Invitational_education&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><span class=\"official-website\"><span class=\"url\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.invitationaleducation.net/\">Official website</a></span></span></li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2208\nCached time: 20180921221251\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: true\nCPU time usage: 0.124 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.180 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 288/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 6475/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 205/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 2765/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 1/400\nLua time usage: 0.056/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.8 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  148.344      1 -total\n 42.14%   62.514      1 Template:Orphan\n 31.97%   47.426      1 Template:Reflist\n 31.28%   46.409      1 Template:Ambox\n 22.49%   33.362      1 Template:Cite_journal\n 22.47%   33.335      1 Template:Official_website\n  3.02%    4.486      1 Template:Monthyear-1\n  1.69%    2.502      2 Template:Main_other\n  1.54%    2.277      1 Template:Monthyear\n  1.49%    2.208      2 Template:PAGENAMEU\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:40909785-0!canonical and timestamp 20180921221251 and revision id 858191537\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","hidden":"","*":"Orphaned_articles_from_October_2016"}